OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FPolice have issued an urgent warning
OL,8,Fto visitors of coastal towns in the
OL,9,Fhot weather after a series of
OL,10,F"unacceptable" disturbances on
OL,11,Fbeaches, roads, and train stations.
OL,13,FParts of the UK, including the North
OL,14,FWest of England, saw the hottest Bank
OL,15,Fholiday Monday on record on 23 May,
OL,16,Fwith temperatures soaring above 30
OL,17,Fdegrees.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
