OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FThousands traveled to local hotspots
OL,8,Fto enjoy the sunshine, but authorities
OL,9,Fsay the subsequent disruption to local
OL,10,Fresidents and businesses was
OL,11,F"unacceptable."
OL,13,FOfficers dealt with "multiple" reports
OL,14,Fof disorder as large crowds attempt to
OL,15,Fmake their way home from the beaches,
OL,16,FMerseyside Police said.
OL,18,FSuperintendent Phil Mullally appealed
OL,19,Fdirectly to day-trippers to remain
OL,20,Fpatient and show respect to the local
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FIn a statement, he said: "We are
OL,8,Freceiving multiple reports of
OL,9,Fdisturbances at train stations, on
OL,10,Fbeaches and the roads.
OL,12,F"While we are dealing with these
OL,13,Freports, the demand and disruption
OL,14,Fbeing caused to other visitors,
OL,15,Fbusinesses and residents is
OL,16,Funacceptable.
OL,18,F"My advice to anyone visiting our
OL,19,Fcoastline today is please be patient
OL,20,Fand respectful as you make your way
OL,21,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,F"Check the following places for any
OL,8,Ftravel advice, cancellations and
OL,9,Fissues on the roads, and please
OL,10,Frespect those who live in these areas."
OL,12,FHe added: "The wonderful weather
OL,13,Fshould be enjoyed, but not at the
OL,14,Fexpense of other people on the roads
OL,15,Fand living in our communities. Thank
OL,16,Fyou for your cooperation and stay
OL,17,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
