OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWith significant congestion reported
OL,13,Fon both the road and rail networks,
OL,14,Ftransport authorities are advising
OL,15,Ftravellers to check live updates
OL,16,Fbefore starting their journeys.
OL,18,FMotorists are also being firmly
OL,19,Freminded of their responsibilities
OL,20,Fwhen choosing where to leave their
OL,21,Fvehicles near coastal areas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
