PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779801070
OL,3,CPolice issue warning over
OL,4,C'unacceptable' behaviour during
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FAuthorities have stated that beach-
OL,8,Fgoing motorists must park responsibly
OL,9,Fin designated areas or they will face
OL,10,Fstrict parking fines from Sefton
OL,11,FCouncil.
OL,13,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,14,Fissued its first amber health alert of
OL,15,F2026, warning that there is a risk of
OL,16,Fa significant impact across health and
OL,17,Fsocial care services.
OL,19,FThe alert will remain in place until
OL,20,F27 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
